commandText:
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Discriminator], [t].[Email], [t].[FirstName], [t].[LastName], [t].[Password], [t].[PhoneNumber], [t].[ProfilePicture], [t].[StudioName], [b].[CarId], [b].[TenantId], [b].[EindDatum], [b].[StartDatum]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[Id], [u].[Discriminator], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[Password], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[ProfilePicture], [u].[StudioName]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    WHERE [u].[Discriminator] = N'Tenant' AND [u].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Bookings] AS [b] ON [t].[Id] = [b].[TenantId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [b].[CarId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Discriminator], [t].[Email], [t].[FirstName], [t].[LastName], [t].[Password], [t].[PhoneNumber], [t].[ProfilePicture], [t].[StudioName], [b].[CarId], [b].[TenantId], [b].[EindDatum], [b].[StartDatum]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[Id], [u].[Discriminator], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[Password], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[ProfilePicture], [u].[StudioName]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    WHERE [u].[Discriminator] = N'Tenant' AND [u].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Bookings] AS [b] ON [t].[Id] = [b].[TenantId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [b].[CarId]
